<br>
Middle Earth was the name of the land of the humans, which was Middle because it was between the realm of the Gods and the Underworld.  I can't remember specifically what either of them are called.<br>
<br>
The Gods lived in their realm, and often fell into combat with the Giants.  Many of the conflicts were caused by Loki, the mischief/trickster guy (who may have been part giant himself?)  <br>
<br>
Shit, I can't remember this well enough to give a decent rendition.  It's fascinating though, I'd recommend checking some of it out. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub12.ezboard.com/urikamaruthedrow.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Rikamaru the Drow</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_lightning.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Tavern Ale Swiller</span><br>  Posts: 59<br> <font color=#6FB8DD>(12/12/01 8:17:17 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Re:</span><hr size=1> what you said about middle earth was completely correct :D<br>
