<br>
There are a lot of fantasy novels out there that use Norse Mythology as a basis.  Tolkien is probably the best example.  Mickey Zucker Reichert has a few books out following Norse legend as well.<br>
<br>
Sorry for the long winded lesson.... too many Thor comic books as a kid I guess.  Norse mythology is much cooler than Greek or Roman mythology imho though so I get carried away. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
